&lt;p&gt;In July 2013 we completed the project related with constructing Agro Biomass Pellet Plant near Vinnytsa, Ukraine. As a part of investment we were responsible for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;establishment of guidelines for the construction of the proposed facility,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;preparation of technological design for a factory with a capacity of 45.000 Mg,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Consultation concerning the modernization of the facilities in order to adapt them to work in a Pellet Agro factory,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Supervision under the montage of technology,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Start the process line and optimization of efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Productivity assumed by the investor was reached on the second day of the start-up technology in the company. Thus, we could confirm again our competence in this type of projects.&lt;/p&gt;
